# Playwright visual snapshot baselines
# These ARE committed — they are the canonical regression baselines for
# `toHaveScreenshot()` assertions. Do NOT add `tests/e2e/*-snapshots/` back.
# (Playwright test run output — HTML reports, traces, screenshots from
# failure-only runs — lives in playwright-report/ and test-results/ which
# remain ignored.)
# tests/e2e/*-snapshots/
.wrangler/

